GEL LOADING DYE 
15% Ficoll 
0.1% Bromphenol Blue 
0.1% Xylene Cyanol 
 
1.  Prepare 10 ml of 15% Ficoll in distilled, sterile water; it may be necessary to incubate 
at 37°C to get the ficoll into solution 
2.  Prepare stock solutions of 1% Bromphenol Blue and 1% Xylene Cyanol in distilled, 
sterile water 
3.  Mix 1 ml of the ficoll with 100 µl of each dye solution (more or less to taste) 
4.  Optional:  add 100 µl of 0.5 M EDTA 

